snippet.textDisplay: I have listened to and watched all three songs Coke Studio Bangla has produced so far. There is a pattern  - the producer starts with an original Bangla song, then mash up with a subordinary song at the end. It must be the case that the producer has been thinking that the supposed fusion adds up. In fact, it does not - rather it degrades the quality of the original song. It happened in all three songs. Sad!
